data.description:
Welcome to this spacious and charming 2-story, 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom pool home nestled in the serene Loxahatchee community. Situated on a sprawling 1.48-acre lot without the confines of an HOA, this property offers a perfect blend of tranquility and modern living. As you enter through the elegant French doors, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that floods in through wide windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the home.The well-appointed kitchen features essential appliances and beautiful granite countertops, making it a hub for culinary enthusiasts.Convenience is key with a main floor bedroom that includes a bathtub and dual sinks, ideal for guests or family members. Upstairs features generous sized bedrooms. The upstairs Master bedroom boasts a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a relaxing tub.

Step out onto the screened balcony and enjoy the great views of the meticulously landscaped yard and inviting pool, perfect for unwinding and entertaining.

Laundry facilities are conveniently located inside, and the attached 2-car garage offers ample space for storage and parking.

The covered patio area is perfect for outdoor dining and relaxation, providing shade and comfort year-round.

Enjoy the Florida lifestyle with a refreshing pool and a fully fenced lot for privacy and security.

This home is ideally situated just minutes away from major transportation arteries such as the Turnpike and I-95, providing easy access to the vibrant communities of Wellington, Boynton Beach, and Downtown West Palm Beach. You're also a short drive from the region's gorgeous beaches and have the convenience of being within reach of three international airports.

Don't miss this unique opportunity to make this delightful property your own, offering the perfect balance of country living with all the modern amenities you desire. Schedule your showing today and experience the best of South Florida living.
